":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36217cc9f706a5bf585fba7382b0880514ab84e","tid":1485790,"uid":22084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登網軍全面進場Reddit Twitter"},{"pid":"c18f8af8c43f9573ed881270b3ab7166e287e26f","tid":1485790,"uid":22084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登網軍全面進場Reddit Twitter"},{"pid":"f664a65f5ba824e56be9d2985a91777c5bdb62b4","tid":1485790,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/flyingshadows/videos/2412061705701511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fflyingshadows%2Fvideos%2F2412061705701511&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=aada09e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/flyingshadows/videos/2412061705701511</a><br />\n\t<br />\n扮示威者收工返警總</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記得有巴打講過紅土遊行之後有班示威者行到旺角警署出面，有一個鬼不斷叫在場人士留低，又不斷話「點解要走呀？」之類嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但明明當日冇計劃過任何嘅圍堵行動，我相信宜家金鐘都係一樣情況，都係有班鬼不斷叫人唔好走，宜家共識都係叫走，到呢一刻喺現場仲叫留低嘅人好大機會係鬼<br />\n<br />\n我可能無能力勸到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我只係希望大家可以智勇雙全，理性啲講，宜家仲keep住要留低嘅仲有啲乜嘢目標？我剩係知道今日嘅戰略目標（搶佔國際輿論）已經超標完成，到呢一刻仲要留低對成個運動仲有乜嘢positive effect ？定係比黑警打一身之後仲要聽日報紙頭版就係衝突畫面？求下你地，大家一齊走，好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後話：<br />\n<br />\n今日總結，我認為大家要互相體諒，畢竟大家都冇上帝視角，有各自嘅限制<br />\n<br />\n例如之前呢三個鐘已經去到金鐘同散咗場嘅巴打，因為擔心前線安危，加上今日目標已經達成，冇必要死守，所以叫走，但始終人已經唔係身處現場，冇上帝視角，望住live 仲見到咁多人，自然開始心急，語氣上亦變得唔係太好<br />\n<br />\n同時之間，前線亦想所有人平平安安走曬，自己最後一批先走，咁當然一定會有鬼從中叫人留低/ 賴死唔走，迫你留低「保護」佢哋，同樣前線亦冇上帝視角，難以判斷係手足定係鬼，散嘅速度自然亦會慢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係呢一句：<br />\n永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e09112c23da5247479962d5a0d763bb9b3c9226","tid":1485790,"uid":22084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登網軍全面進場Reddit Twitter"},{"pid":"104da553133a4e55ef867f57f108baf447db6a40","tid":1485790,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:49:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">POPO 螢光棒</span></strong>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ccabb70557e9a6cdfb19d0851f10e33ec34206","tid":1485790,"uid":22084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:49:44.000Z","msg":"Tui!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登網軍全面進場Reddit Twitter"},{"pid":"732bf8f0f6308ce6c7ad9d3c4f7bbe3f804808bc","tid":1485790,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:50:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e37196397d12785b9227646424c20422baf